"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwoocommerce_marketplace=self.webpackChunkwoocommerce_marketplace||[]).push([[196],{7579(e,a,n){e.exports=n.p+"assets/img/general-settings.0ff9e2c4.webp"},7948(e,a,n){n.r(a),n.d(a,{comp:()=>s,data:()=>r});var t=n(641),i=n(7579);const o={},s=(0,n(6262).A)(o,[["render",function(e,a){return(0,t.uX)(),(0,t.CE)("div",null,[...a[0]||(a[0]=[(0,t.Fv)('<h1 id="configuration-–-general-settings" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#configuration-–-general-settings"><span>Configuration – General Settings</span></a></h1><p><img src="'+i+'" alt="Admin Panel"></p><p>After successfully installing WooCommerce Marketplace, the admin can configure the core marketplace settings such as vendor registration, approval workflow, default vendor capabilities, and overall marketplace behavior from:</p><p><strong>Marketplace &gt; Settings &gt; General</strong></p><hr><h2 id="general-settings-options" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#general-settings-options"><span>General Settings Options</span></a></h2><h3 id="default-commission" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#default-commission"><span>Default Commission</span></a></h3><p>The <strong>Default Commission</strong> is applied when no commission is set specifically for a vendor.</p><h4 id="example" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#example"><span>Example</span></a></h4><ul><li>Product Price: <strong>$100</strong></li></ul><p>If the default commission is <strong>20%</strong>:</p><ul><li>Vendor receives: <strong>$80</strong></li><li>Admin commission: <strong>$20</strong></li></ul><hr><h3 id="deduct-discount-from" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#deduct-discount-from"><span>Deduct Discount From</span></a></h3><p>If a discount is applied by the customer, this option defines how the discount amount is adjusted.</p><p>Available options:</p><ul><li>Both vendor total amount and admin commission amount</li><li>Vendor total amount only</li><li>Admin commission amount only</li></ul><hr><h3 id="auto-approve-vendor" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#auto-approve-vendor"><span>Auto Approve Vendor</span></a></h3><p>If enabled, vendors will be <strong>automatically approved</strong> after registration.</p><h4 id="example-1" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#example-1"><span>Example</span></a></h4><ul><li>When enabled, any user signing up as a vendor is instantly converted into a vendor.</li><li>When disabled, admin approval is required before the user becomes a vendor.</li></ul><hr><h3 id="separate-vendor-dashboard" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#separate-vendor-dashboard"><span>Separate Vendor Dashboard</span></a></h3><p>If enabled, vendors will have a <strong>separate dashboard</strong>, similar to the admin dashboard, for managing their marketplace activities.</p><hr><h3 id="data-delete-after-vendor-delete" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#data-delete-after-vendor-delete"><span>Data Delete After Vendor Delete</span></a></h3><ul><li>If enabled, <strong>all vendor data</strong> will be deleted when the vendor is removed.</li><li>If disabled, the vendor’s data will be <strong>assigned to the admin</strong> instead.</li></ul><hr><h3 id="applicable-shipping-methods" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#applicable-shipping-methods"><span>Applicable Shipping Methods</span></a></h3><p>The admin can select which shipping method will apply at checkout:</p><ul><li><strong>Admin Shipping Method</strong></li><li><strong>Vendor Shipping Method</strong></li></ul><hr><h4 id="more-about-applicable-shipping-methods" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#more-about-applicable-shipping-methods"><span>More About Applicable Shipping Methods</span></a></h4><h5 id="admin-shipping-method-selected" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#admin-shipping-method-selected"><span>Admin Shipping Method Selected</span></a></h5><ul><li>Admin shipping rates will apply to <strong>all products</strong>, including vendor products.</li><li>The shipping rate remains the same regardless of whether the cart contains admin or vendor products.</li></ul><h5 id="vendor-shipping-method-selected" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#vendor-shipping-method-selected"><span>Vendor Shipping Method Selected</span></a></h5><ul><li>Vendor-specific shipping rates will apply to vendor products.</li><li>Admin shipping applies to admin products.</li></ul><h5 id="mixed-cart-admin-vendor-products" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#mixed-cart-admin-vendor-products"><span>Mixed Cart (Admin + Vendor Products)</span></a></h5><p>If the cart contains products from <strong>both admin and vendor</strong>:</p><ul><li>The total shipping cost will be a <strong>combined rate</strong> of both admin and vendor shipping.</li><li>This applies regardless of the selected Applicable Shipping Method.</li></ul><hr><h3 id="select-vendor-page" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#select-vendor-page"><span>Select Vendor Page</span></a></h3><p>Select the page to be used as the <strong>Vendor Page</strong>.</p><p>⚠️ <strong>Important Notes</strong>:</p><ul><li>Updating a new vendor page will <strong>erase existing content</strong> of the selected page.</li><li>After changing the vendor page, <strong>update permalinks</strong>.</li></ul><hr><h3 id="shop-name-on-registration" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#shop-name-on-registration"><span>Shop Name on Registration</span></a></h3><ul><li>If set to <strong>Required</strong>, vendors must enter a <strong>Shop Name</strong> during registration.</li><li>If set to <strong>Optional</strong> and left empty, the module will use the <strong>Vendor Name</strong> as the shop name.</li></ul><hr><h3 id="shop-url-on-registration" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#shop-url-on-registration"><span>Shop URL on Registration</span></a></h3><ul><li>If set to <strong>Required</strong>, vendors must enter a <strong>Shop URL</strong> during registration.</li><li>If set to <strong>Optional</strong> and left empty, the module will use the <strong>Shop Slug</strong> as the vendor’s username.</li></ul><hr><h3 id="vendor-terms-conditions-page" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#vendor-terms-conditions-page"><span>Vendor Terms &amp; Conditions Page</span></a></h3><p>The admin can select a <strong>Terms &amp; Conditions page</strong> that will be displayed to vendors during registration.</p><hr><h3 id="allow-vendor-registration-on-my-account" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#allow-vendor-registration-on-my-account"><span>Allow Vendor Registration on My Account</span></a></h3><ul><li>If enabled, vendor registration fields will appear on the <strong>WooCommerce My Account</strong> signup form.</li><li>If disabled, a link to the <strong>Seller Central Registration Form</strong> will be displayed instead.</li></ul><hr>',59)])])}]]),r=JSON.parse('{"path":"/documentation/configuration-general-settings.html","title":"Configuration – General Settings","lang":"en-US","frontmatter":{},"headers":[{"level":2,"title":"General Settings Options","slug":"general-settings-options","link":"#general-settings-options","children":[{"level":3,"title":"Default Commission","slug":"default-commission","link":"#default-commission","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Deduct Discount From","slug":"deduct-discount-from","link":"#deduct-discount-from","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Auto Approve Vendor","slug":"auto-approve-vendor","link":"#auto-approve-vendor","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Separate Vendor Dashboard","slug":"separate-vendor-dashboard","link":"#separate-vendor-dashboard","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Data Delete After Vendor Delete","slug":"data-delete-after-vendor-delete","link":"#data-delete-after-vendor-delete","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Applicable Shipping Methods","slug":"applicable-shipping-methods","link":"#applicable-shipping-methods","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Select Vendor Page","slug":"select-vendor-page","link":"#select-vendor-page","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Shop Name on Registration","slug":"shop-name-on-registration","link":"#shop-name-on-registration","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Shop URL on Registration","slug":"shop-url-on-registration","link":"#shop-url-on-registration","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Vendor Terms & Conditions Page","slug":"vendor-terms-conditions-page","link":"#vendor-terms-conditions-page","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"Allow Vendor Registration on My Account","slug":"allow-vendor-registration-on-my-account","link":"#allow-vendor-registration-on-my-account","children":[]}]}],"git":{"contributors":[{"name":"nikhilsharma.qa322","username":"","email":"nikhilsharma.qa322@webkul.in","commits":5}],"changelog":[{"hash":"ecd0ef7f219b32e811d160d7aa559c703813b434","time":1769682443000,"email":"nikhilsharma.qa322@webkul.in","author":"nikhilsharma.qa322","message":"update the blog"},{"hash":"65c53321324899821dcd64e73bf33635d31ac8f5","time":1769611166000,"email":"nikhilsharma.qa322@webkul.in","author":"nikhilsharma.qa322","message":"update the blog"},{"hash":"b6ee22ebc488139bc13e516ed6bfe20f33251889","time":1769513415000,"email":"nikhilsharma.qa322@webkul.in","author":"nikhilsharma.qa322","message":"update the blog"},{"hash":"d9597ee06a0b33451054ae852159899b77c05a4f","time":1768991677000,"email":"nikhilsharma.qa322@webkul.in","author":"nikhilsharma.qa322","message":"update the blog"},{"hash":"aca65ba8aa97aabc334b2e4bb1cf75cb68704317","time":1768982436000,"email":"nikhilsharma.qa322@webkul.in","author":"nikhilsharma.qa322","message":"create the vuepress blog content"}]},"filePathRelative":"documentation/configuration-general-settings.md"}')}}]);